Silver and Strong Copper having carefully had a debate, Strong Copper had the lead over Silver in @wDN{Enlil's} house -- Father @wDN{Enlil} be praised!

@(13-29=c536.I.13) Then the days passed, the year grew long, the silos filled up and flax was beaten ……. The year, the faraway days, ……. The heavens …… stars and lengthening shadows. …… the shadows ……. The stars of heaven …… did not ……. The records, to be found in the sacred tablets of the stars, ……. The heavens, ……, having been separated from the earth …….

$ (8 lines fragmentary)
